summary: An ordinance vacating a portion of Bagley Avenue lying southeasterly of a line thirty-five (35) feet southeasterly from and parallel with the center line of Northlake Avenue, as established by Ordinance No. 33626, and a portion of an unnamed street lying between blocks seven (7) and eight (8), Bagley's Addition to the City of Seattle, on petition of the Pacific Ammonia and Chemical Company, et al.
